{"tid":1651380,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【抗爭妙法】成本小、效用大","createTime":"2019-10-13T10:27:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T17:50:04.000Z","uid":300510,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d1978c3b5134ddb120d17e38317780be677f8810","tid":1651380,"uid":300510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T10:27:20.000Z","msg":"轉頭硬物並不能令全副武裝的黑警懼怕<br />\n相反嘔心物，如「屎蛋、臭蛋」等&hellip;更能令一般人退避和恐懼<br />\n相信會對黑警造成一定的心理壓力<br />\n若然有任何裝備受到染污<br />\n定必馬上想卸下惡臭的隨身裝備<br />\n從而進一步影響其他同袍心態<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">（相信你都唔會坐響個周身屎臭嘅人旁邊）</span><br />\n<br />\n重點集中對付<br />\n「狗車」的門柄及窗邊這些必須經常接觸的位置<br />\n令嘔心物更容易散播開其他地方，冷氣入口位置（前方或車頂位置）<br />\n<br />\n「狗屋」的通風系統，如冷氣機、抽氣扇、鮮風入口位置<br />\n停車場、外牆、大門入口及窗亦可，目的令整幢建築物臭氣熏天！<br />\n<br />\n只要大家齊心，毎人自製10至20隻「屎蛋、臭蛋」<br />\n相信數量一定相當可觀<br />\n非常期待「屎蛋」如雨下的情境招呼黑警<br />\n和事後中招的黑警的狼狽表現<br />\n<br />\n最後送上一則伊索寓言《風和太陽》作為參考<br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/news/g9e6yle.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fnews%2Fg9e6yle.html&d=uxh%2FksCcDU8UuFRsnlXnuYTtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=ec578b32\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/news/g9e6yle.html</a><br />\n<br />\n噁心的臭蛋<br />\n<a href=\"https://elite0905.pixnet.net/blog/post/25928800\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Felite0905.pixnet.net%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F25928800&d=uxh%2FksCcDU8UuFRsnlXnuYTtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=28415270\" target=\"_blank\">https://elite0905.pixnet.net/blog/post/25928800</a><br />\n<br />\n如何自製臭雞蛋（須時較長）<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikihow.com/%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C%E8%87%AD%E7%82%B8%E5%BC%B9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikihow.com%2F%25E5%2588%25B6%25E4%25BD%259C%25E8%2587%25AD%25E7%2582%25B8%25E5%25BC%25B9&d=uxh%2FksCcDU8UuFRsnlXnuYTtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=c7f36ace\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikihow.com/%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C%E8%87%AD%E7%82%B8%E5%BC%B9</a><br />\n<br />\n如何自製屎蛋（即成）<br />\n1. 在雞蛋頂端刺穿一個小洞<br />\n2. 用針筒抽出一半蛋液<br />\n3. 用針筒注入糞便混合<br />\n4. 最後用熱溶膠密封小洞"},{"pid":"8369da46007b42c098bc45842d3d11c97572f3ba","tid":1651380,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T10:31:18.000Z","msg":"之前可樂同咖啡都推唔郁<br />\n你個idea哂氣喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a664845ab24fd8d0457c4d563ca4683b1b7efa","tid":1651380,"uid":300510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T10:33:36.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9992f2f198b5879a0c75dbc353ee9540e20846a3","tid":1651380,"uid":300510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T13:37:51.000Z","msg":"自推2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"754d480acfc29369b17483d568db96fa076a0269","tid":1651380,"uid":300510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T17:50:04.000Z","msg":"自推3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}